title: Walmart.com: Igloo 5 Gallon Cooler Just $18.44 (Great For Outdoor Parties)
text:
Great for camping and Summer parties! Head to Walmart.com and grab this Igloo 5-Gallon Beverage Cooler for just $18.44. These are so nice to have for camping, days at the lake, or backyard BBQs, and these coolers keep water cold up to three days! This seems like a great deal seeing as Amazon has this on sale for $22.99 for Prime Members only .
